Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.12,0:00:04.23,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,STAFF ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.62,0:00:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A meeting of delegates?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.62,0:00:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently there's been such an \Ninflux of clubs since Spring,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.35,0:00:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we've run out of club rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.83,0:00:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the outbreak of Wizard War VI\Nfor basal supremacy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.38,0:00:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.59,0:00:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence! And...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.79,0:00:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the student council \Nis gathering all of the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.40,0:00:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,clubs  to hold a one-time briefing session.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.08,0:00:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They want your club to be in attendance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.81,0:00:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the purpose of that meeting to take away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.35,0:00:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nrooms from clubs deemed inactive?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.52,0:00:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.38,0:00:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.44,0:00:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The meeting is being held today after school,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.03,0:00:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nso make sure your delegate attends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.57,0:00:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the club's delegate, Togashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.70,0:00:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.68,0:00:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it you, Rikka?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.98,0:02:17.82,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,CLUB\NDELEGATES\NMEETING
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.54,0:02:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Sabbath hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.82,0:02:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The universal decision-making body!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.54,0:02:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this where world-wide trends are created?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.59,0:02:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They all look so intimidating.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.26,0:02:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because each club is desperate\Nto secure a club room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.35,0:02:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do this, Rikka?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:39.55,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,CLUB\NDELEGATES\NMEETING
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.40,0:02:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dekomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.23,0:02:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.55,0:02:46.10,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,CLUB\NDELEGATES\NMEETING
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.77,0:02:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From this day forward \Nstarting now, Dekomori...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.71,0:02:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I transfer leadership of the\NFar-East Magical Society to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.63,0:02:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.03,0:02:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a napping society!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.74,0:02:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a being of the Dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.93,0:02:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is terribly perilous for one such as I\Nto appear
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.27,0:02:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in such an overt gathering.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.25,0:02:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't wanna do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.04,0:02:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta, if I should appear in such a meeting,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the overwhelming power of Wicked Lord Shingan
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.12,0:03:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nwill inevitably affect every mortal in my vicinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying you don't wanna do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.22,0:03:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.97,0:03:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.64,0:03:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The meeting is starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you should have gone in\Nwith her, Togashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I could do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.40,0:03:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only one delegate from each club can attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.74,0:03:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, you are a shining example\Nof a Dark Being!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.06,0:03:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just look at your all-enveloping \Ndeep black aura!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.91,0:03:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can touch you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.41,0:03:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's just nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.87,0:03:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I call the delegate from the\NFar-East Magical Napping...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.31,0:03:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Society...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.46,0:03:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...summer thereof.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.13,0:03:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is I. I am here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Please describe your club activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.71,0:03:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately I am not at \Nliberty to discuss that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.30,0:03:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who have chosen to learn of our society
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.76,0:03:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have done so in full acceptance\Nof the risks to life and limb...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.81,0:03:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but with the guidance \Nof the fallen angels...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.65,0:04:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you did write a speech for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.86,0:04:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, because we can't let her do the talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.36,0:04:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We, the "Far-East Magical Napping Society\N- summer thereof"...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.53,0:04:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...mumble, mumble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such commoners!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.33,0:04:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those weaker beings were awed speechless
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.88,0:04:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the presence of Wicked \NLord Shingan. Victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My master! Your dark aura is\Na force to be reckoned with!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.59,0:04:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she was removed from the room\Nwithout saying anything helpful?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.41,0:04:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's more like she removed herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.51,0:04:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Based on the historical materials\Nof magic and such...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.59,0:04:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we explore the cultural \Nvalue and uses of...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.59,0:04:38.26,Copy of Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you please speak up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.81,0:04:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.86,0:04:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.56,0:04:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.48,0:04:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you go in there with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.57,0:04:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because only one person\Nfrom a club could attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is exactly the time to use\Nthe fact that you're a couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:04:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.12,0:05:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka and I are of one flesh!\NOnly together are we one person!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.58,0:05:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one must ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.21,0:05:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...come between us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.38,0:05:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be too embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.34,0:05:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you two are inseparable. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.51,0:05:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're such lovebirds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.01,0:05:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In what way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We really would be\Nejected if we did that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.71,0:05:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.02,0:05:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.31,0:05:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A special news bulletin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.53,0:05:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The student council?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.78,0:05:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh. The gist was that you don't\Nappear to be active enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.17,0:05:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to merit the use of a club room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.12,0:05:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They asked me for my opinion as your advisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.41,0:05:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's no big surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Give that back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what came of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told them that I would confirm \Nyour club's activities
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.25,0:05:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and make a one-time report.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.19,0:05:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do you guys do in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.51,0:05:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.72,0:05:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.76,0:05:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are our advisor, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.43,0:06:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The student council person\Nasked me the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.10,0:06:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you have a magic summoning circle,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.52,0:06:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nso I'm sure you do magic-type things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.61,0:06:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.03,0:06:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mjolnir Tornado!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.86,0:06:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.28,0:06:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.74,0:06:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nap?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.83,0:06:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It's even in the name, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.21,0:06:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Napping Society - summer thereof."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.08,0:06:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. Does that mean\Nyou're also a napping club?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.17,0:06:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.21,0:06:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt that classifying our magical society
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.91,0:06:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nas a napping society will help our case much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.80,0:06:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.42,0:06:39.75,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Napping Competition\N(search)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.49,0:06:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Napping clubs are perfectly acceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.58,0:06:42.25,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,10 Ways to Win a Napping Tournament\NThe Napping Olympics Expo
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.72,0:06:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is such a thing \Nas championship napping?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. In Europe, they even hold tournaments\Nas a competitive sport.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:47.34,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Registering Now\NFor This Year's Participants
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.65,0:06:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you determine the merits of a nap?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the total score is based on...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...speed of repose, sleep posture,\Nslumber depth...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:06:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and time to achieve wakefulness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:07:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew about this, Kumin-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.87,0:07:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, because I am involved in nap studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.57,0:07:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I happen to be acquainted
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.25,0:07:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with a teacher at a school that has
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.24,0:07:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nwhat they call the Siesta Appreciation Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Siesta?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.34,0:07:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.46,0:07:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly, Master! It means "nap" in Spanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, for example, if we \Nwere to actively enter an
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,intramural competition with that school...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.56,0:07:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The council would be forced \Nto accept our club.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.06,0:07:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:33.68,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,To:      Momijigaoka High \NSchool Siesta Club Advisor
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.14,0:07:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like me to send an email\Nasking the other school to compete?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.44,0:07:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, please! Or at least I'd like to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.90,0:07:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but Kumin-senpai is the only one\Namong us who actually naps.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.20,0:07:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't jump straight into a competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.82,0:07:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. It's not really that hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.83,0:07:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you how to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.45,0:07:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.79,0:07:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! Just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.46,0:07:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darkness comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.21,0:07:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.34,0:07:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out for the trains!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.75,0:07:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea that napping was so profound.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.84,0:08:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is. It's very difficult\Nto achieve an elegant nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.43,0:08:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The top, most active performers\Nachieve such elegant naps...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.91,0:08:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's emotionally moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.94,0:08:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.35,0:08:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Their posture and the\Ncomfortable look on their faces...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.19,0:08:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The indescribably delicate depth of sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...as they enter deep slumber.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.07,0:08:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, they look just like...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.45,0:08:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.91,0:08:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all we've heard, she's actually\Nstarting to look impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.19,0:08:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.59,0:08:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.71,0:08:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.84,0:08:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the members of\NIcho High's napping club?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.23,0:08:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.81,0:08:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Nemuri Sui and I represent Momijigaoka\NHigh's Siesta Association...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.65,0:08:52.13,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,President, Siesta Association:\NSui Nemuri
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.27,0:08:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? The Siesta Association?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.44,0:08:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this sleepy aura emanating\Nfrom her every pore?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.28,0:09:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is drowsiness personified!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.91,0:09:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Master! You'll be sucked in!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dekomori!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.62,0:09:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My advisor passed along\Na rare invitation to compete...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I thought I should\Nintroduce myself in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.05,0:09:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you taking the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.67,0:09:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.51,0:09:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.59,0:09:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears it was unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.97,0:09:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.30,0:09:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From what I can determine,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.00,0:09:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you do not appear to be \Nseriously involved in napping.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.35,0:09:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only presume that you use your club\Nas an excuse to goof around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.81,0:09:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She knows!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.15,0:09:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.03,0:09:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost every club that claims \Nto be a nap club are like yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.65,0:09:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, our Siesta Association is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.99,0:09:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We take napping very seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.83,0:09:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please refrain from making such\Ninvitations for amusement.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.46,0:09:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.75,0:09:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:10:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The competition is called off.\NPlease notify your advisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.05,0:10:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is not for amusement.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.05,0:10:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nor are we goofing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.68,0:10:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kumin-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.18,0:10:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Far-East Magical Napping Society\N- summer thereof...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.77,0:10:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...always takes its activities seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.35,0:10:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Togashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dekomori!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.90,0:10:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.11,0:10:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.74,0:10:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.58,0:10:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.12,0:10:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I accept this as an actual challenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.83,0:10:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.12,0:10:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear on the Wicked Lord Shingan\Nthat I always fight for keeps.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.38,0:10:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Failure equals death!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.96,0:10:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're on fire, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.84,0:10:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we should happen to lose this battle,\Nat that very moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.47,0:10:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I will disband our society!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.68,0:10:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How stupid are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.65,0:11:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to learn to stop being so haphazard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.57,0:11:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle is always waiting to pounce unbidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.91,0:11:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.83,0:11:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an official playing field?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.29,0:11:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Sanctioned by the Japanese high\Nschool napping federation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.63,0:11:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The professional version is a little bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.52,0:11:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professional?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.30,0:11:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Team competitions are fought\Nwith five people to a team.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.42,0:11:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Points are awarded for the speed of falling
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nasleep and for artistic merit and posture.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.47,0:11:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's surprisingly complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.22,0:11:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now let's give it a try!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about posture for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.52,0:11:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think only about sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.65,0:11:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have Theatre Club to go to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.98,0:11:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment you leave,\Nour club is as good as disbanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.86,0:11:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.32,0:11:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not all that easy to fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.83,0:11:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Start by closing your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.92,0:12:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Takanashi I hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.31,0:12:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.05,0:12:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on Earth is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.85,0:12:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.85,0:12:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.02,0:12:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong! I was just, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.83,0:12:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.07,0:12:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's sleep paralyzed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.57,0:12:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.92,0:12:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master's mind is free of \Nthe wicked and indecent
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.45,0:12:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nthoughts experienced by the likes of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never said anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.75,0:12:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what do you mean by indecent?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.21,0:12:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.96,0:12:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Early bloomer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.63,0:12:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You be quiet, Fake Summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock that off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.34,0:12:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.97,0:12:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Sleep properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.18,0:12:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, we will nap outdoors.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.31,0:12:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ability to sleep the \Nsame, despite a change
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:13:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nof environment, is a vital napping skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.06,0:13:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.31,0:13:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to sleep here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.77,0:13:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master! The light! The \NLight Being is attacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Schwarz Shield Prototype...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.34,0:13:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Mark IV!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.62,0:13:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now let's swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.12,0:13:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.49,0:13:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, because comfortable fatigue\Nis the best method to induce a good nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.54,0:13:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why the pool? It's \Nstill too cold to swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.34,0:13:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. That's a shame.\NSwimming really is the best way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because swimming helps you "crawl" into bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.30,0:13:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a pun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.97,0:13:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Isshiki? What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.77,0:13:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably followed Kumin-senpai to the pool
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.96,0:13:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nto show off to her that he can nap too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.07,0:13:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.03,0:13:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.28,0:13:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kumin-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.62,0:13:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naps are a lot harder than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.87,0:14:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's hard to ready, set, nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.41,0:14:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. Wicked Lord \NShingan is all powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.87,0:14:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my master!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.42,0:14:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is now really the time for that?\NIf we lose, the club is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.21,0:14:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just need to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.68,0:14:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Win, Yuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.37,0:14:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.03,0:14:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I know we can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.39,0:14:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where does that unwavering\Nconfidence come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.23,0:14:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dekomori, nice timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.65,0:14:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you rigging up now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.27,0:14:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we really going to make it like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.48,0:14:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't we work out some sort of strategy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.36,0:14:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What strategy could there be\Nin a sleeping competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.11,0:14:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aside for learning how to sleep faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.95,0:14:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! There is a simple way to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.71,0:14:46.17,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,The Night Before the\NCompetition
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will fight at your side...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...until the darkness vanishes with the dawn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.71,0:14:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.25,0:14:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just have to stay up all night...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.43,0:14:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and we'll definitely be sleepy\Nin time for the competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.72,0:14:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.76,0:14:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although it isn't the most elegant\Nnapping method.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.76,0:15:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't control our actions \Nafter we're asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.77,0:15:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so it's more important to\Nstart with falling asleep faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.27,0:15:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.85,0:15:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, enjoy yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.65,0:15:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.15,0:15:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.61,0:15:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why? Why does this always happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fork them over, Very Poor Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.16,0:15:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this! The Parallel \NPin Bone King explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Not my fish paste factory!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.83,0:15:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,50 combo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.83,0:15:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.71,0:15:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a sparkling monochrome monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.39,0:15:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.89,0:15:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.89,0:15:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WHAT THE HECK?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.16,0:16:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.83,0:16:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Togashi, what did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.37,0:16:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.95,0:16:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has the Dark Flame Master\Nturned to the dark side?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.71,0:16:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So sorry. Old habits die hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.96,0:16:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot that Hero and the Wicked Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.52,0:16:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shingan are bound by the Lover's Contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe this is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WHAT THE HECK?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.10,0:16:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.71,0:16:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.10,0:16:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.14,0:16:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Throw down salt! I need salt, Kuzuha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.44,0:16:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But weren't all of you \Nsupposed to stay awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.99,0:16:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I failed! This was the\Nmagical devil girl's plot all along!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.22,0:16:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's our fault for falling asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.74,0:16:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.95,0:16:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will now commence the practice match...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.54,0:16:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...between Icho High's Far-East Magical\NNapping Society - summer thereof...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.16,0:16:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...versus Momijioka High Siesta Association.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.84,0:16:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.85,0:16:58.16,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Advance Guard: Fujiko Nasutaka
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.35,0:16:59.66,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Second Guard: Barumu Ichiba
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.88,0:17:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think we have a hope in hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.85,0:17:01.16,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Center: Youko Tenbaku
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.35,0:17:02.62,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Second in Command: Toromi Utsutsutouge
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.40,0:17:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible to determine\Nif they're even awake at this very moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.60,0:17:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are definitely dwellers \Nof the Dream World.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.81,0:17:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.85,0:17:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As promised, you will disband if you lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.86,0:17:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would be happy to obliterate...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.99,0:17:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...even one more farcical napping club.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.28,0:17:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.91,0:17:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we can win this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.08,0:17:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We all got so much sleep,\Nour skin looks fabulous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.50,0:17:28.93,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Advance Guard: Rikka Takanashi\NSecond guard: Sanae Dekomori
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.08,0:17:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have only one option left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.92,0:17:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Center: Yuta Togashi
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.62,0:17:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we apologize to them now, just maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.63,0:17:34.78,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Second in Command: Shinka Nibutani
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.04,0:17:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.34,0:17:38.44,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain: Kumin Tsuyuri
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.63,0:17:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will not lose.\NOur club is not that irresponsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.07,0:17:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kumin-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.51,0:17:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember thinking it\Nwhen I met Rikka for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.93,0:17:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.51,0:17:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our true goal is to locate \Nthe invisible boundary line.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.94,0:17:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But our actions will not end there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.40,0:18:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For that is our society!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.15,0:18:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a feeling back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.34,0:18:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that things really could work out\Nif I joined her and her friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.84,0:18:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With her? But she has chunibyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.25,0:18:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. But you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.66,0:18:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I know nobody\Nreally gets this about her...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.23,0:18:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but she's very wholehearted and
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.90,0:18:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,serious about what she does...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.27,0:18:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...just like a napping club.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.84,0:18:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kumin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.97,0:18:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In our Far-East Magical Napping Society\N- summer thereof...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.35,0:18:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we nap hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.89,0:18:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we play hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.14,0:18:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and we banish hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.24,0:18:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we cannot lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.19,0:18:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're invincible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.82,0:18:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.26,0:18:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be destroyed, real.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.27,0:18:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blow up, synapses.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.39,0:18:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Banishment, This World!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.25,0:19:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This world of sleep belongs to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.63,0:19:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave here at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.47,0:19:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Avalon Smasher!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.23,0:19:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mjolnir Hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.85,0:19:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disqualified!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.57,0:19:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the Dark Flame Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.25,0:19:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be enveloped in the flames of darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disqualified!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.87,0:19:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does it always have to be me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.12,0:19:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a cramp in my leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disqualified!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.51,0:19:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's left?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.97,0:19:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.76,0:19:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Non-REM killer technique:\NCircadian Rhythm Destroyer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.47,0:19:52.19,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,The Non-REM Killer Technique:\NCircadian Rhythm Destroyer
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.85,0:19:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destiny Ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destiny Ring
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.77,0:19:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.09,0:20:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could take that incredible power
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.44,0:20:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nand aim for the world title if you were serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.78,0:20:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, I like that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.66,0:20:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.41,0:20:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why I must protect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.38,0:20:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sleeper's Wake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.64,0:20:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kumin-senpai. Kumin-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.52,0:20:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Togashi, you're all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.77,0:20:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it. We won.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.40,0:20:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kumin, I am grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.95,0:20:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? What happened to Sui and her friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.49,0:20:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They went home. They said they accept defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.33,0:20:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means we don't have to disband.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.58,0:20:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.79,0:21:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will battle Fake Summer\Nonce again tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.15,0:21:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.46,0:21:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.76,0:21:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a funny dream while I was sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.01,0:21:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.64,0:21:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was with all of you, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.26,0:21:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that really a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.35,0:21:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I unleash this power.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.65,0:21:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning Blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.90,0:21:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, the attributing\Nthunder technique is flawless.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.90,0:21:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it! Count me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.64,0:21:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Freshman, you messed with my costume again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.33,0:21:36.30,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,FAKE
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.49,0:21:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are, Fake Summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.08,0:21:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very versatile.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.33,0:21:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.96,0:21:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not look away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.92,0:21:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimately nothing changed.\NWe still don't nap at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.61,0:21:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but I'm happiest when I sleep here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.26,0:21:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.05,0:21:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.35,0:21:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta, watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.06,0:22:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.98,0:22:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dekomori, sound the lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.30,0:22:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Be\NContinued
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.39,0:22:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.52,0:22:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me!
